RawBytePacket
RawBytePacket

A class that contains packet information about an Inertial packet

Types
MIP Packet Bytes
INVALID_PACKET

Start of packet found, but packet was invalid

DATA_PACKET

Complete data packet

COMMAND_PACKET

Complete command or command response packet

NO_PACKET_FOUND

No packet was found in these bytes

MIP Packet Information
FROM_READ

The packet was read from the device

FROM_SEND

The packet was sent to the device

Payload

typedef for the bytes that make up a payload in a packet
